column5: ....Thers lots of new "news" in the OFC News.
I read it, nice that it's there.

Regarding "Missing link in Lake Huron food chain threatens health of salmon, whitefish "  Most of us that fish both the Sarnia and Kincardine areas of Huron have been saying as well as pointing this out for 4 to 5 years.  Nice to see someone finally got around to taking us seriously.
